         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne Botanic Garden ¶ 25th March 1871 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to solicit that you will sanction the transfer of a sum of Fifty five pounds — £55 — from the Vote for Wages to Gardeners to the ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">71.03.25d<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James McCulloch</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Y71/3695, unit 576, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Written by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">name?</seg>, and signed by M.</p>
               </note>Melbourne Botanic Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">25th March 1871</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to solicit that you will sanction the transfer of a sum of Fifty five pounds — £55 — from the Vote for Wages to Gardeners to the Vote for Stores, Stationery, Timber &amp;c. This latter vote, which had already been considerably reduced in 1870, was lowered still more for 1871, and is inadequate to meet the demands of the Department. A considerable sum had to be transferred last year to the Wages vote, as heavy expenditure had been incurred in the beginning of the year before reductions now made; therefore I consider it but just, that the very much needed transfer of the above mentioned sum may be made from this vote.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I beg to enclose requisition for coals for the engine and hot houses, for paper &amp;c. for the museum, and for flowerpots.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Director Botanic Garden</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Honorable the Chief Secretary<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>McCulloch minuted his approval for the requests, under which, in an unknown hand, was added: '(requisition approved. Papers to be returned early).'<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">there is no date for the approval.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
